Today I’m gonna show you some cool items from my wardrobe, I call them the “basics,” - Jeans
T-shirts, 
and “investments,” such as-
Skirts
Blazers
Blouses
*They can be tailored specifically for the body-type*- and is the easiest way to guarantee that every outfit look amazing on you.

With all the make-up videos I make, my only motive is to help all of you lovely ladies out there to create your personal style. 
And now this 💁‍♀ It’s all about inspiration and getting inspired by someone. 
I would really love if that someone can be ME in ANYONE’S life. 💝
